title: Thanks Obama
description: The fellas thank Obama for courageously violating COVID restrictions, play Veep or Veep, and welcome two guests: Sen. Mike Crapo to talk taxes and Dr. Marty Makary with an update on the Delta variant.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Josh Holmes, Sen. Mike Crapo, Comfortably Smug, Dr. Marty Makary, Michael Duncan)
